<PageTitle>Help – metrics glossary</PageTitle>

<div class="container py-3">
    <h1 class="mb-3"><i class="bi bi-question-circle text-purple" aria-hidden="true"></i> Help – metrics glossary</h1>
    <p class="lead">
        This page explains every value that NetLine collects from your devices.
        Next to each metric in the results tables you will find an
        <i class="bi bi-info-circle" aria-hidden="true"></i> icon that links straight to the matching entry below.
    </p>

    <nav aria-label="Table of contents" class="card shadow-sm my-4">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h2 class="h5 mb-3">Table of contents</h2>
            <ul class="list-unstyled mb-0">
                <li><a href="#kategoria-ping">Availability (Ping)</a></li>
                <li><a href="#kategoria-dns">DNS</a></li>
                <li><a href="#kategoria-port">Network ports</a></li>
                <li><a href="#kategoria-net-if">Network interfaces</a></li>
                <li><a href="#kategoria-cpu">CPU</a></li>
